54
00:02:48,280 --> 00:02:49,360
Come on in.

55
00:02:49,520 --> 00:02:50,320
Come.

56
00:02:50,320 --> 00:02:51,280
Master Meng.

57
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:52,800
These are the prettiest girls

58
