I need to talk to you.

65
00:03:14,920 --> 00:03:15,720
Well,

66
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:18,200
I like you.

67
00:03:20,160 --> 00:03:20,960
Lu Ye,

68
00:03:21,480 --> 00:03:23,720
