Aren't you drinking with Lu?

85
00:05:43,480 --> 00:05:45,160
It's getting late.

86
00:05:45,480 --> 00:05:48,000
You help Lu upstairs to the guest room.

87
00:05:51,360 --> 00:05:55,680
Sir, I'll take my leave.

88
00:05:56,400 --> 00:05:57,200
Okay.

89
00:06:08,640 --> 00:06:09,960
Follow him.

90
