Zhang Wange.

95
00:06:50,040 --> 00:06:51,168
You wanted to be a painter!

96
00:06:51,280 --> 00:06:52,680
Why are you here?

97
00:06:56,800 --> 00:06:58,520
Is it strange?

98
00:06:58,520 --> 00:07:00,560
