113
00:09:08,480 --> 00:09:09,440
Leave with me.

114
00:09:10,880 --> 00:09:12,560
This place isn't right for you.

115
00:09:22,520 --> 00:09:23,200
Remember.

116
00:09:24,240 --> 00:09:25,240
Stay hidden in the room.

117
00:09:25,240 --> 00:09:26,240
Don't go outside.

118
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:46,800
Zhang Wange.

119
00:09:50,440 --> 00:09:52,040
Zhao Si will take you away later.

120
00:09:52,040 --> 00:09:53,680
You'd better behave yourself.

121
00:09:53,680 --> 00:09:54,600
You hear me?

122
00:10:04,520 --> 00:10:05,640
So noisy.

123
00:10:25,400 --> 00:10:26,720
Prepare to die!

124
00:10:38,480 --> 00:10:39,600
Zhang Wange!

125
00:10:45,320 --> 00:10:47,480
Someone! Get a doctor!

126
00:10:47,840 --> 00:10:48,920
Lu Ye.

127
00:10:50,880 --> 00:10:52,280
Don't save me.

128
00:10:53,960 --> 00:10:54,960
Why?

129
00:11:05,200 --> 00:11:09,160
