I am a policeman.

132
00:11:15,240 --> 00:11:16,680
So, don't worry.

133
00:11:17,240 --> 00:11:18,440
You will be okay.

134
00:11:19,960 --> 00:11:21,200
You'll be fine.

135
00:11:22,720 --> 00:11:24,920
(I've been living a meaningless life.)

136
00:11:25,800 --> 00:11:27,280
(Thank you)

137
00:11:27,480 --> 00:11:30,720
(for ending this miserable life.)

