(I still came back too late.)

149
00:13:35,400 --> 00:13:37,800
(It was him. He attempted to harass me.)

150
00:13:37,800 --> 00:13:38,400
Zhang Wange.

151
00:13:38,400 --> 00:13:38,920
He's evil!

152
00:13:38,920 --> 00:13:40,800
They saw you attack me.

153
00:13:40,800 --> 00:13:42,000
You'll rot in jail!

154
00:13:42,000 --> 00:13:42,800
I swear!

155
00:13:45,120 --> 00:13:45,920
Chief Editor,

156
00:13:46,480 --> 00:13:48,400
