157
00:13:48,400 --> 00:13:48,800
Mom.

158
00:13:48,800 --> 00:13:49,680
Wange is still young.

159
00:13:49,680 --> 00:13:50,360
Get up.

160
00:13:50,360 --> 00:13:51,360
I did nothing wrong.

161
00:13:51,360 --> 00:13:53,360
