169
00:14:08,960 --> 00:14:10,080
All the girls are here.

170
00:14:12,000 --> 00:14:13,120
Take that one.

171
00:14:14,000 --> 00:14:17,600
(She'll be the first test subject
for the Corn Poppy.)

172
00:14:22,160 --> 00:14:22,880
Zhang Wange.

173
00:14:22,880 --> 00:14:23,600
You deliver this.

174
00:14:23,600 --> 00:14:24,800
Okay.

175
00:14:24,800 --> 00:14:26,120
Chief Editor wants to see you.

176
00:14:27,000 --> 00:14:28,040
Alright.

177
00:14:31,280 --> 00:14:33,320
(I really traveled back
three years ago.)

178
00:14:34,120 --> 00:14:35,920
