223
00:16:44,280 --> 00:16:44,680
Behave!

224
00:16:44,680 --> 00:16:45,320
Please spare me.

225
00:16:49,680 --> 00:16:52,000
Thank you. I'm glad you are here.

226
00:16:52,680 --> 00:16:53,280
You're welcome.

227
00:16:53,920 --> 00:16:56,080
After all, I'm the second son
of the Pei family.

228
00:17:04,400 --> 00:17:05,200
Hello.

229
00:17:05,200 --> 00:17:07,400
Mr. Pei, I've encountered some trouble.

230
00:17:07,400 --> 00:17:08,960
You know anyone at the police station?

231
00:17:12,680 --> 00:17:13,440
Mr. Pei.

232
00:17:13,440 --> 00:17:16,120
