236
00:17:24,080 --> 00:17:24,920
missing girls.

237
00:17:26,760 --> 00:17:27,440
By the way,

238
00:17:27,720 --> 00:17:29,000
since I helped you so much,

239
00:17:29,560 --> 00:17:30,360
how do you thank me?

240
00:17:32,240 --> 00:17:33,800
