251
00:18:22,240 --> 00:18:23,160
(This is my painting.)

252
00:18:26,080 --> 00:18:26,800
Pei Xun.

253
00:18:26,800 --> 00:18:29,400
Why did you give my painting
to Zhou Nian?

254
00:18:29,920 --> 00:18:31,040
(Your theft)

255
00:18:31,040 --> 00:18:33,160
(made my life miserable.)

256
00:18:33,560 --> 00:18:35,760
(From now on,)

257
00:18:35,760 --> 00:18:37,320
(I'll take back)

258
00:18:37,320 --> 00:18:39,320
