261
00:18:41,520 --> 00:18:41,960
You'll see.

262
00:18:41,960 --> 00:18:42,640
Really?

263
00:18:43,000 --> 00:18:44,200
Sorry, guys, I'm late.

264
00:18:45,240 --> 00:18:47,640
Pei Xun, you're so late.

265
00:18:50,104 --> 00:18:51,322
(Zhou Nian, Daughter of the Zhou Family)

266
00:18:57,600 --> 00:18:59,840
Who is this lady?

267
00:19:01,360 --> 00:19:02,360
Do you want to tell him?

268
00:19:10,080 --> 00:19:10,960
Zhang Wange.

269
